<html>

<body>
   <h1>Java to Javascript Converter</h1>

   <div id="intro">
      Welcome to the free online Java to JS converter.
      <br/>
      Java code is converted into readable Javascript code
      using the StrataCode Java to JS converter.
      <p/>
      Supports:
      <ul>
         <li>Java 1.8 syntax with a subset of Java 1.6 utility libraries, some implemented by hand in
          javasys.js and some converted from the Apache utils with minor edits in jvsys.js.
         <li>All Number types in Java represented as the one JS number type.
      </ul>
      <div class="note">
         This online form only supports class-at-a-time conversion for standalone classes using a subset of Java utils.
         To convert a complete project, <a href="https://www.stratacode.com/download">download</a>
         the free + open source 'scc' command and follow
         <a href="https://www.stratacode.com/doc/javaToJS.html">these instructions</a>.
      </div>
   </div>
   <p/>

   <div id="mainForm">
       <div id="sourceSideBySide">
          <div>
          Enter Java Code for one class<br/>
          <textarea id="inputTextarea" rows="40" cols="80" changeEvent="=: inputSrcText = value"
                    value="=: inputSrcText = value"/>
          </div>
          <div>
          Result Javascript:<br/>
          <textarea id="resultTextArea" rows="40" cols="80"><%= resultSrcText %></textarea>
          </div>
      </div>

       <br/>
       <div id="licenseAgreement">
          This software is provided free for limited use based on the resources available on a small, private VPS.
          <br/>
          Conversion is provided 'as is' with no express or implied warranty and we assume no liability for damages caused through the use of this software.
       </div>
       <br/>
       <input id="doCvtButton" value="Convert Java to JS" type="button" clickEvent="=: doConvert(0)"/>

      <br/>
      <div id="errorsView" visible=":= inputErrors != null && inputErrors.length() > 0">
         Errors from input file:
         <pre id="errorMessagesView"><%= inputErrors %></pre>

         Warning: any unresolved type references are left untranslated in the generated code
      </div>

      <br/>
      <div id="depsView" visible=":= jsFiles != null && jsFiles.size() > 0">
         Generated JS requires these dependencies:
         <div id="jsFilesView" repeat=":= jsFiles" repeatVarName="jsFile">
            <a href=":= jsFilePrefix + jsFile"><%= jsFile %></a>
         </div>
      </div>
   </div>

   <style type="text/css">
      #sourceSideBySide {
         display: flex;
         flex-direction: row;
      }
      #licenseAgreement {
         font-size: 80%;
      }
      #errorsView {
         font-color: #cc1212;
      }
      .note {
         font-style: italic;
         font-size: 90%;
      }
   </style>

</body>

</html>
